# Privacy Policy - Qahwty

## Privacy Policy

At Qahwty, we take your privacy seriously. We collect only the data necessary to deliver your orders and manage our services.

---

## What We Collect

- Full name
- Phone number
- Delivery address
- Order details

**We do not collect or store any banking or payment data**, since all payments are handled upon delivery only.

---

## How Your Data is Used

Your personal data is **never shared** with third parties without your explicit consent. It is used solely to process your orders and improve our services.

---

## Data Security

We use industry-standard security measures to protect your information.

---

